Class Summary
AMDPickedEvent Event signaling that an AnnotatedMapDescriptor has been picked.
AnnotatedMapDataLoadedEvent Event signaling annotated map data has been loaded.
CpdDstDisambiguatedEvent Event indicating that the destination compound has been disambiguated in the case of the same synonym referring to multiple Compounds.
CpdDstPickedEvent Event indicating that a destination compound has been picked
CpdSrcDisambiguatedEvent Event indicating that the source compound has been disambiguated in the case of the same synonym referring to multiple Compounds.
CpdSrcPickedEvent Event indicating that a source compound has been picked
ExperimentUploadEvent Event indicating that an experiment data upload has either been requested or has succeeded.
LoadingEvent Event indicating the state of a long loading event, where long is defined by the implementor
LogInEvent Event indicating that a user has logged in.
LogOutEvent Event indicating that a user has logged in.
MapElementClickEvent Event indicating an element of the map has been clicked
MapUpdateEvent Event indicating that the map has been panned or zoomed
OrganismPickedEvent Event indicating that an organism has been picked
OrganismUploadEvent Event indicating that an organism upload has been requested or has succeeded.
PanZoomControlEvent Event fired from the PanZoomControl, indicating the intended transform to be applied to map.
RoutePickedEvent Event indicating a route has been selected
RouteStepPickedEvent Event indicating a route step has been selected.
SamplePickedEvent Event indicating an experiment Sample has been selected.
SearchTargetEvent Event indicating a search target has been found.
ViewResizedEvent Event indicating that a View has been resized.
 

Enum Summary
